{
  "texts": [
    "Different models vary from the default DenseGNN architecture as follows: Model 1 removes LOPE node embeddings; Model 2 removes the DCN networks; Model 3 replaces all DCN-GC layers with SchNet-GC layers; Model 4 replaces all DCN-GC layers with GIN-GC layers.",
    "The reference model, representing the default DenseGNN architecture, is highlighted in bold.",
    "\"GCL\" indicates the number of Graph Convolutional (GC) layers.",
    "npj Computational Materials | (2024) 10:292"
  ]
}